metadata.name: CYBER RED
metadata.description:
She looks so hot! But so harsh... This is Cyber Red. She was meant as a character who quite likely got out of fighting games. She looks so original, and I'm sure that if you meet her in games, she will become your favorite character. 

Each Cyber's has its own story. Red was meant as a freestyle wrestling fighter. There is fire and fury burning in her. She can protect herself always and everywhere, she can handle any difficulties and any obstacles. She considers herself special, the strongest and most independent. Red shows it with his whole appearance, that behind a beautiful face lies a huge power.
